hort url embed in website image short url account tools  add to data list get email notification notes source world bank   release world development indicators   units  current dollars not seasonally adjusted frequency  annual notes gdp at purchasers prices is the sum of gross value added by all resident producers in the economy plus any product taxes and minus any subsidies not included in the value of the products it is calculated without making deductions for depreciation of fabricated assets or for depletion and degradation of natural resources data are in current us dollars dollar figures for gdp are converted from domestic currencies using single year official exchange rates for a few countries where the official exchange rate does not reflect the rate effectively applied to actual foreign exchange transactions an alternative conversion factor is usedsource code nygdpmktpcd suggested citation world bank gross domestic product for republic of korea mktgdpkranwdb retrieved from fred federal reserve bank of st louis httpsfredstlouisfedorgseriesmktgdpkranwdb july   related content related resources real gdp per capita in the republic of korea south korea discontinued household debt to gdp for united states geofred map gross domestic product for republic of korea alfred vintage series gross domestic product for republic of korea related categories gdp national accounts indicators korea republic of south korea countries international data sources more releases from world bank releases more series from world development indicators tags korea world development indicators world bank gross domestic product annual not seasonally adjusted nation release tables × confirm delete are you sure you want to remove this series from the graph this can not be undone cancel remove × browse data close × permalinkembed done × save graph to user account save graph save as new graph cancel × retrieving data × updating graph filter    services fred® alfred® geofred® fraser® ideas resear